Austrian GP: Lewis Hamilton takes pole in tricky conditions
Watch highlights as Mercedes driver Lewis Hamilton masters the tricky conditions in Austria to claimpole position at the Red Bull Ring.Hamilton was 0.2secs quicker than team-mate Nico Rosberg, with both Mercedes drivers spinning off the track on their final flying laps.Ferrari's Sebastian Vettel was third from Williams's Felipe Massa, with Nico Hulkenberg an impressive fifth for Force India.Available to UK users only.